<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Magic Alumni</title>

    <link href="~/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url('/Background-image/AlumniBackground1.jpg'); /* Path relative to wwwroot */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #fff; 
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px; 
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95); 
            color: #000; 
            border-radius: 15px; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); 
            transition: transform 0.2s; 
        }

            .card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px); 
            }

        .btn {
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 20px; 
        }

        footer {
            color: #ddd;
        }

        .header-container {
            margin-top: 5rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

            .header-container h1 {
                font-size: 3rem; 
                font-weight: bold; 
            }

            .header-container p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                font-weight: 300;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container text-center header-container">
       
        <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Magic Alumni</h1>
        <p class="lead">Connect, share, and engage with alumni from your institution.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        
        <div class="row mt-4">

            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Admin</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Admins play a critical role in overseeing and monitoring all alumni activities within the platform
                            and managing locations such as Country, State, and City.
                        </p>
                        <a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="AdminHome" asp-area="AdminArea" class="btn btn-success">Go to Admin</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Company Admin</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            The Company Admin is responsible for managing and controlling alumni activities for the institution.
                            They can activate or deactivate members and students, organize events, handle event registrations, manage polls and responses, and define the rules
                            and regulations for alumni engagements.
                        </p>
                        <a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="CompanyAdminHome" asp-area="CompanyAdminArea" class="btn btn-primary">Go to CompanyAdmin</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

           
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Member</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Members are the heart of Magic Alumni. They can register
                            and log in to the platform, view and register for events, participate in polls, send and accept
                            connection requests, and expand their network by maintaining connections with friends and peers.
                        </p>
                        <a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="MemberHome" asp-area="MemberArea" class="btn btn-info">Go to Member</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        
        <footer class="mt-5">
            <p class="text-muted">&copy; 2024 Magic Alumni. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

   
</body>
</html>
